{"tid":1861372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"最可怕嘅係種族滅絕緊，而我地仲係懵然不知","createTime":"2020-02-04T06:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:43:03.000Z","uid":135871,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22c7d913e4f0d17915704745013c77934d220763","tid":1861372,"uid":135871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無睇過呢張圖。其實我地<strong>極有可能已經經歷緊第九階段</strong>，用種族滅絕去解釋點解政府唔封關，唔派口罩，仲要係社區到起隔主離營，成件事就好合理，<strong>因為佢地根本就係想香港人死</strong>。係反送中嘅示威入面，我地已經令到港共同中共嘅醜態盡現，今次疫症就係佢地要滅絕香港人嘅一個最好機會。現今世代已經無可能再用實槍實彈去做種族滅絕，用武漢肺炎呢個疫症去消滅香港人，就係佢地最好嘅方法，唔單只唔會受到國際制裁，更加可以展示俾國際社會睇其實澳門做得比香港更好，令外資轉投澳門，透過榨乾香港嘅最後一滴經濟去回血，應對貿易戰帶黎嘅影響，同時懲罰港人。<br />\n<br />\n正因為咁，我希望大家可以唔出街嘅就唔好出街啦，同醫護一齊罷工。留住條命仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1342472721acc439cd34656ba489ea4758cd8c42","tid":1861372,"uid":135871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/